privacyPro_menuTitle.title: Privacy Pro
privacyPro_menuTitle.note: Used as a label in a customization menu

privacyPro_signedOutSubtext.title: Blocked tracking attempts will appear here. Keep browsing to see how many we block.
privacyPro_signedOutSubtext.note: Placeholder for when we cannot report any blocked trackers yet

privacyPro_feedCountBlockedPlural.title: {count} tracking attempts blocked
privacyPro_feedCountBlockedPlural.note: A summary description of how many tracking attempts were blocked by DuckDuckGo in the last 7 days when there is more than one. E.g., '1,028 tracking attempts blocked.

privacyPro_nonsubscriber_subtext.title: Try PrivacyPro for free today!
privacyPro_nonsubscriber_subtext.note: Used when user is not a subscriber

privacyPro_otherCompanyName.title: Other
privacyPro_otherCompanyName.note: A placeholder to represent an aggregated count of entries, not present in the rest of the list. For example, 'Other: 200', which would mean 200 entries excluding the ones already shown

privacyPro_otherCount.title: {count} attempts from other networks
privacyPro_otherCount.note: An aggregated count of blocked entries not present in the main list. For example, '200 attempts from other networks'
